{"word":"G2323 - θεραπεύω - therapeúō - ther-ap-yoo'-o - Cure","slug":"G2323","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θεραπεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>therapeúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ther-ap-yoo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cure"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - therapeuo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ther-ap-yoo'-o</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/G2324\">G2324</a>; to <i>wait upon</i> menially, that is, (figuratively) to <i>adore</i> (God), or (specifically) to <i>relieve</i> (of disease): - cure, heal, worship."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2322\">G2322</a>"}]}